Note there are two different issues.  One is:  Do you find male/male sex disgusting while finding female/female sex erotic?<br>
<br>
Two is:  Do you find male/male sex not allowable while finding female/female sex allowable?<br>
<br>
One is a personal preference, two is a double standard.  Don't mix these two viewpoints up.  The difference there is *critical*.  It is possible to find both allowable while finding only one (or neither) attractive.<br>
<br>
I can't stand shrimp, or liver, but would never think of denying others the right to either.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dahlisss>dahlisss</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 22<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/25/03 10:44 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm62.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=686.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: yeah another Gay thread. *try to be mature and civil*</span><hr size=1> I agree two women is generally more acceptable and it is a double standard.  But most people find the female body MUCH more attractive than a mans.  My wife has told me that and several other women as well when the topic came up.  Maybe that is why it is more acceptable??  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :\ --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/ohwell.gif ALT=":\"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=siava>Siava</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.knology.net/~ahnmei/savepoint.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I'm an Asshat lady. <br>
